title: [Firefly Villa, South Catwalk]
description: Floorboards of polished linden glitter with a golden glow as the sunlight reflects off of them, while hummingbirds flit amongst the wisteria vines that twine about the carved railings.  Viridian sails slant across the space to create a bit of shelter from the island's harsher elements, their ends anchored to both the distant wall of the inn and the tree beyond.

Floorboards of polished linden glitter with a silver glow as the moonlight reflects off of them, while fireflies flit amongst the wisteria vines that twine about the carved railings.  Viridian sails slant across the space to create a bit of shelter from the island's harsher elements, their ends anchored to both the distant wall of the inn and the tree beyond.
